  "name": "Deploy - Modern (Restful) API",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"deploy-modern-restful-api\">Deploy - Modern (Restful) API </h1>\n<p><span><span>This article explains how to deploy the Modern (Restful) API once a signed contract has been received and paid for (1st payment of pp or full amount):</span><br/></span></p>\n<p><span>Generating the Key</span></p>\n<p>Email Development Team Leader to request that they generate the key for the relevant Retail Express database.</p>\n<p>You will receive a response such as:</p>\n<p>API Key: SoQxC4a3D24kSAcFYM9Om5ESUujdr7m8aAFqkttt</p>\n<p>Limits: 5,000 requests per day, 10 requests per second, burst 50</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span> Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1. Add a new ticket</p>\n<p>2. Add the email address for the contact on the solutions agreement</p>\n<p>3. Select the macro <strong>Finance &gt; ??</strong></p>\n<p><em>Information for this can be found via the following link:</em><br/><br/><em><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.retailexpress.com.au%2F\">https://developer.retailexpress.com.au/</a></em><br/><br/><em>From there simply click on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.retailexpress.com.au%2Fapis\">API Explorer</a> and then <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.retailexpress.com.au%2Fapis%2Fvd0ld51rce\">Retail Express API</a> and click on the green 'Authorise' icon and enter the following API Key</em><br/><br/><em> DpULVzAXIw7AgG3bx2vtY1h0H6ve8U1b8qB2APub</em><br/><br/><em>Please note that it is Limits: 5,000 requests per day, 10 requests per second, burst 50</em></p>\n<p><em><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978635/API_Explorer.PNG\" alt=\"API_Explorer.PNG\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=30