15/Retail_Express_API.PNG 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978615/Retail_Express_API.PNG 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978615/Retail_Express_API.PNG 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978615/Retail_Express_API.PNG\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002081276/Authorize.PNG\" alt=\"Authorize.PNG\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002081276/Authorize.PNG 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002081276/Authorize.PNG 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002081276/Authorize.PNG 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002081276/Authorize.PNG 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002081276/Authorize.PNG 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002081276/Authorize.PNG 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002081276/Authorize.PNG\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></em></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978655/API_Key.PNG\" alt=\"API_Key.PNG\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978655/API_Key.PNG 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978655/API_Key.PNG 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978655/API_Key.PNG 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978655/API_Key.PNG 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978655/API_Key.PNG 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978655/API_Key.PNG 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001978655/API_Key.PNG\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>4. Replace the [ClientId] section with the Client ID from Retail Express</p>\n<p>5. Submit the ticket as <strong>Solved</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
